title: Rinne leads Predators past Oilers 2-0
text: BING NEWS: Rinne leads Predators past Oilers 2-0 NASHVILLE, Tenn. - (AP) -- Pekka was perfect. Pekka Rinne made 31 saves to help the Nashville Predators beat the Edmonton Oilers 2-0 on Saturday night.
